Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:56.95,Default,Poco,0,0,0,,Gaogaoík?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaogao—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:15.39,Default,Manabu,0,0,0,,Jsem Gaogaoík...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.72,Default,Souta,0,0,0,,Studííí!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.77,Default,Souta,0,0,0,,To bylo těsný...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.42,Default,Souta,0,0,0,,Přichází příliv.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:27.26,Default,Souta,0,0,0,,Kdy jsem to odpadl—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:28.70,Default,Souta,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:31.86,Default,Souta,0,0,0,,Poko?
